OL,3,CSouth Tyneside Council opens skip drop-
OL,4,Coff points amid bin strike disruption
OL,6,FSkips have been made available for
OL,7,Fresidents in South Tyneside to drop
OL,8,Foff their household waste, following
OL,9,Fongoing bin strike disruption.
OL,11,FSouth Tyneside Council has set up
OL,12,Ftemporary waste drop-off points at
OL,13,Fnine locations across the borough over
OL,14,Fthe weekend.
OL,16,FIt comes as refuse workers will be
OL,17,Ftaking their sixth round of strike
OL,18,Faction on Tuesday 2 April to Friday 5
OL,19,FApril, over allegations of bullying
OL,20,Fand mismanagement.
