OL,6,FA South Tyneside Council spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "We understand how frustrating
OL,8,Fand challenging the situation is for
OL,9,Fall our residents and thank everyone
OL,10,Ffor their continued patience. We are
OL,11,Fworking hard to mitigate the impact of
OL,12,Fthe strikes as much as we can.
OL,14,F"We are aware of the concerns relating
OL,15,Fto the build-up of waste and that
OL,16,Fresidents are being affected by the
OL,17,Fongoing action short of strike taken
OL,18,Fby waste collection crews.
