OL,6,F"General waste presents a greater
OL,7,Fpublic health risk which is why we are
OL,8,Fasking all residents to present their
OL,9,Fgrey household waste bin only for
OL,10,Fcollection every day, from Tuesday 26
OL,11,Fto Friday 29 March, until it is
OL,12,Fcollected.
OL,14,F"We are also reintroducing temporary
OL,15,Fweekend waste drop-off sites, this
OL,16,Ftime to help residents dispose of both
OL,17,Fexcess household and recyclable waste."
