OL,6,FSkips will operate from 9am to 3pm,
OL,7,Ffrom Friday 15 March to Sunday 17
OL,8,FMarch, and again from Friday 22 March
OL,9,Fto Sunday 24 March at:
OL,11,FThe general waste drop-off points are
OL,12,Ffor bagged domestic household waste
OL,13,Fonly.
OL,15,FThe council has also increased the
OL,16,Fnumber of booking slots - by more than
OL,17,F2,000 per week - at the Recycling
OL,18,FVillage at Middlefields Industrial
OL,19,FEstate, South Shields.
